Program: Outlook
Title: The Prisoners Trapped by Hurricane Katrina
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03kbsj1
Last Broadcast Date: Not available
Controversy over what happened to prisoners trapped in their cells during Hurricane Katrina in New Orleans last year. Also, the resurgence of bicycles in Malawi as fuel costs rise. Listeners' reaction to an item on sex tourism. Finally adventurers Jo and Rob Gambi on their marriage, their expeditions and living with cancer. Show less